Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:05.28,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:13.32,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,下面即将开始的就是这次[火龙诞生祭]的主角 [造物主们的决斗的最终决战]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:22.61,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,主持和审判则由 千眼专属裁判黑兔来主持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:26.70,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对了 白夜叉 干嘛吧黑兔的裙子弄的总是看不见里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,半走光什么的 也太老土了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.45,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没想到你居然不理解真正的艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.13,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:42.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,所谓的艺术就是每个人对未知领域的想像力 对神秘事物的探求心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:48.64,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对 不属于任何事物的艺术就是 你在这个宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.49,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,在这个宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,女孩子的裙下风光也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看见了则只是粗俗的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看不见就是艺术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.32,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看不见 就是艺术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:07.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,现在就让我们一同见证 这个奇迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:09.57,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,白夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.21,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,别看了 会被传染的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:19.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是的 明明等下春日部就要开始比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:26.41,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,Rattenfinger 哈梅尔的吹笛人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,难道这个孩子就是魔王的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:31.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:35.41,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没事 这是不可能的啦
Comment: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:10.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,(OP)
Comment: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:15.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,第8话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:14.73,122,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(1000,0)}翻译:pan712 \N 时间轴:灰机舞 \N 后期:zht \N 压制:小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:14.73,mondaiji title,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fsp7\pos(630,682)\fad(1000,0)}不吉利的事情貌似和笛子的乐曲一起来了哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}关于鬼火 我就知道这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,希望能帮得上你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是你真的不需要任何帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,规则可是允许找一个伙伴一起比赛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.16,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小姐加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.65,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么就让各位选手入场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.77,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这位就是无名的春日部耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,春日部加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.40,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有鬼火的爱夏·伊格尼法特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:01.98,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看见没 无名的家伙吓地都坐在地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.05,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么杰克 就用你那奇葩的笑声来嘲笑她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.02,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咿哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.85,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这个 难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:16.49,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没错 这家伙就是我们鬼火最棒的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,著名的怪物 杰克南瓜灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,十六夜 快看是杰克啊 真正的杰克南瓜灯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:28.29,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,居然能看到实物 真是太令人激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我知道了 淡定点  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:34.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让你与爱夏大人我同台竞技 还不哭著感谢一下么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你这个无名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:45.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,以主办人之名 为你们准备比赛场地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.17,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么了 这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.96,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,空气变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哇 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.29,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个巨大的树根里就是游戏的舞台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:14.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么她们会有一场怎么样的比赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,恩惠游戏名称 安德伍德的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说要从这个树根组成的迷宫中出去么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.36,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把对方的恩惠破坏就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么我宣布 现在恩惠比赛正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:41.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好啦 你先走吧 面对无名可不需要我这么认真比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你是鬼火的头领么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:48.34,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,诶 你觉得我是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:54.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是虽然爱夏大人我不是头领 可大家都听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.89,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么偷跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:00.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好啊 既然你耍阴招 我就来真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:04.22,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,杰克 我们走 在这迷宫中狩猎无名喽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.73,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你全身都是破绽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.45,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,杰克 烧死她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.81,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 真敏捷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.73,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,和仁说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.84,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,原来如此 天然瓦斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:55.94,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的 鬼火的传说是在无人的地方燃起青色的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:04.18,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是所谓的鬼火 但是其实是因为土地产生的天然瓦斯自燃的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.65,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这种小把戏 在小姐的鼻子面前 一下子就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.28,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,鬼火的头领是出现在生与死之间的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 我就无法正面对决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是她不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.41,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么 这个游戏 能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.84,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 这个小丫头 知道出口么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对啊 通过空气流动明白了出口的方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.77,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 剩下的就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.49,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,给我用全力 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.84,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,失礼了 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.13,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,爱夏 你快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:57.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.49,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:13.17,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对 在生与死之间现身的大恶魔 维拉·札·伊格尼法特斯的最高杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:18.60,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我就是杰克南瓜灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:26.20,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,鬼火的火焰就是恶魔的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:33.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为了让人类也能理解 我们故意放出比较科学的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,通知他们有尸体埋在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.92,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那是因为爱夏是操纵大地天然瓦斯的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:52.09,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,本来是地缚灵的她 是由我们的头领所收养的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,通过引导想爱夏这样的灵所攒下的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:03.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,使我们的存在和共同体都壮大了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,来吧 所持系统树的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:13.85,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不死的怪物 杰克南瓜灯就是你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.64,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这就是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.40,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,春日部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:34.28,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,即便是春日部 面对不死 就没法破坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:45.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.21,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,胜者 爱夏·伊格尼法特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.85,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我能问一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:07.93,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这次的比赛 没有想过请别人帮忙么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:08.78,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你的瞳孔中透露出些许寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:20.62,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,既然在共同体中了 依靠别人的情况是经常会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:27.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,作为一个南瓜 我太多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:35.32,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 你啊 我可没觉得这样就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:40.16,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,下次再见到你 可就是爱夏大人我的完胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.22,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,给我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:53.97,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真的啊 我如果能再给点更好的建议就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.92,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,比赛辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.60,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,各位对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:00.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:07.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那家伙 即使没有赢得比赛 但是也有所收获
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.20,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是非常精彩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你有一个很好的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是啊 果然春日部很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对吧 十六夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:23.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.94,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,黑色的契约书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.46,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.53,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,参加者是在场的全部共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,主办人指定白夜叉为参加者头领
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.40,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,主办人方胜利条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.16,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,杀死所有参加者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.05,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,参加方胜利条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,识破虚伪的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,指出真实的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.45,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魔王出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.22,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么就开始游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.84,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魔王来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.30,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,居然这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:53.89,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,白夜叉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.61,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,珊多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.42,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,十六夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.93,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说魔王出现么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:12.93,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没事啦 你快躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,快看 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.64,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,出现了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:35.01,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,城市的混乱还有白夜叉的事就交给你处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拜托他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.25,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,难道十六夜你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.25,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我就去和魔王打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,威悉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魔王大人我想见你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.62,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,别小看我 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:18.01,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没想到被你夺走先机 还有点能耐么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.94,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我成绩单上的评价可是 [总是让人非常意外]啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,威悉 快把他解决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:31.81,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啰嗦 拉婷你先降下去 要是在这磨蹭会被主人骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.32,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.73,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真不懂啊 为何放她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:44.18,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这点东西 你肯定一下就能破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,打倒你之后再慢慢追喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:50.17,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,威悉河的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.37,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(458,661)}老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.37,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉婷还有哈梅尔的威悉河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说答案只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:02.93,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你们就是根据哈梅尔的吹笛人的传说而诞生的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:09.36,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,由杀死一百三十个儿童的方法而灵化的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:18.22,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,根据哈梅尔的传说 有诱拐 神隐 或者绞杀 还有自然灾害等说法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:26.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你把这个墙壁扭曲的力量 可以推测应该是塌方之类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.69,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.81,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,识破虚伪的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.21,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,指出真实的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:39.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这个胜利条件其实就是让我们找出哈梅尔的真相么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.53,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我还以为你就是个臭小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.16,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没想到脑筋倒是挺好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:55.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有就是 我不是魔王 只是个爪牙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:16:00.78,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是么 那么前菜就得快点解决才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.14,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你真的是吸血鬼的纯血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:12.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,修特罗姆 已经足够了 我不要她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,修特罗姆 也就是暴风么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.73,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么他就是和天灾有关的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我要去找本命了 杀了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.30,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:39.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然很疼 但是还是原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:55.68,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有 收回前言 和你应该能成为好同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:11.22,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我等你很久了 火龙的珊多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你就是哈梅尔的魔王么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:23.01,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 你搞错了 我的恩赐名是黑死斑魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,作为守护秩序的人 我绝对不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.57,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是么 阶层统治者还真是有勇气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,各位 不要慌乱 先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:46.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大家不要慌乱 我们可是高尚的火龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.25,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没有事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,要掌握好力道 不杀死他们还这是难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.61,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.02,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 南瓜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.81,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,白夜叉 这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.13,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:32.81,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是多半是因为契约文书导致我不能参战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.53,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,根据契约文书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:40.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你们听好了 把我现在说的话 一字不差地传达给黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:47.96,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,第一 这个契约文书在最开始可能就存在条件的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.69,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最坏的情况 这个游戏可能无法胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.01,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:19:00.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,第二 要告诉她这个共同组很可能是新建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.89,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,第三 把我封印的方法大概就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.42,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好了 说够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:13.36,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,诶呀呀 最强的阶层统治者也没办法出手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 对火龙的人做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.48,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这种事情当然是保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.76,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有你们很碍事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.94,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有一套么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:30.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,春日部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.62,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:41.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:47.25,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,吹笛子 操纵老鼠的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拥有比常人更好的听觉成了弱点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:59.18,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是随意啦 你现在开始就是我的手下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,仁君 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,带著春日部到黑兔那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你以为我会让你逃走么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,所有人都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.78,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你这个小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.17,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:25.70,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.10,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然仅仅一瞬间 但是却能够束缚我的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.17,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你的力量还真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:39.42,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真丢脸 要是能有春日部一半的运动能力就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.45,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刚才的孩子也不错 不过你更加有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.33,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我可是知道你有多强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是这份力量还请你今后为我们而使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.64,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么 序章就到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.18,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哈梅尔的吹笛人出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这才只是一个开始而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:46.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对的 让我们开始演奏最美妙的歌剧吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:31.52,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,说起来 先有白萝莉 然后是金发萝莉 现在还出来个斑点萝莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:34.01,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,别说的那么轻松啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:37.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是 黑兔你的腿更加有魅力啊
